# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# .env.example — Invoice PDF Editor
#
# HOW TO USE (local development only):
#   1. Copy this file:   cp .env.example .env
#   2. Fill in the real values in .env
#   3. NEVER commit .env  (it is already in .gitignore)
#
# On Render (production):
#   Set these in Dashboard → Environment → Add Secret File / Environment Variable
#   Do NOT put real keys in render.yaml or any committed file.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Required only for AI Mode (✨ toggle on the website).
# Leave blank to use Rule-Based mode only — the app works fine without it.
# Get your key at: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...your-key-here...

# Optional: override the default OpenAI model (default is gpt-4o-mini)
# OPENAI_MODEL=gpt-4o-mini
